{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":35342,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"dz也是知识分子吗？","timestamp":1593013121,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35343,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"那应该怎么办","timestamp":1593013129,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35348,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不要说怪话","timestamp":1593013146,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35351,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"犬儒？","timestamp":1593013162,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35353,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 承认社会现实，寻求解决方案","timestamp":1593013178,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35355,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"手中无权的都是幻想，所以应该问为何权力中心和知识分子之间总是有很大鸿沟？","timestamp":1593013186,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35356,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 我非常不想成为 知识分子...","timestamp":1593013201,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35368,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 权力中心为什么不应该和知识分子有距离？","timestamp":1593013282,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35378,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"__的通病就是__，把当_成_。这一点在_中可见一斑。","timestamp":1593013345,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35385,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: ？我谔谔","timestamp":1593013360,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35511,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"身边即世界的话，感觉清华里面很多人对偏底层一点的社会缺少认知... ","timestamp":1593014210,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35916,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"除了批判还能怎样，走上街头闹xc？社会问题大多不是知识分子造成的，而我们也可以成为资本或其他什么的狗，批判很多时候反而是关心社会的表现。只能说不能为了批判而批判，并为此洋洋得意。","timestamp":1593016676,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":36107,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"老一辈知识分子确实会幻想自己可以\"底层人民\"，会把批判当成正确，当然，随着教育的普及，这种做法越来越没人care了。我个人不认可知识分子就高人一等，就一定要去启蒙底层劳动人民。知识分子做好自己专业内的事就好了。","timestamp":1593017706,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":36119,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"上面第一句打少了，应该是启蒙\"底层人民\"","timestamp":1593017770,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":36228,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"批判是知识分子的重要社会功能，尤其是相关领域的知识分子。至于之后有没有别的什么，短时间来看这应该是当局者的事了","timestamp":1593018434,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":36457,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Jason: 恕我直言，不给出解决方案的批判就是纯粹的扯淡","timestamp":1593019686,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":83609,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":5820,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 你不如说是提出了喧嚣的参考建议，无论正向或反向。当局者的知识与思想是有限的，有时候这种有限是致命的。能够在繁杂的信息中进行筛选并做出合理的决策是优秀当局者的必要品质","timestamp":1593857814,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":5820,"reply":17,"tag":null,"text":"知识分子的通病就是用幻想代替社会现实，把批判当成解决手段。这一点在最近大学顶替案的舆论中可见一斑。","timestamp":1593013072,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782585,"url":"","vote":{}}}